FILE: parser.rs
MOD: stanza/parser
ROLE: Single-stanza XML parser — extracts routing headers from opening tag, preserves raw XML verbatim
EP: parse
STAB: stable
INV:
  - parse() extracts only from=, to=, type=, status=, mentions= attributes
  - The 'raw' field in MessageStanza/PresenceStanza is the ORIGINAL input string — never modified
  - Attribute values are captured by [^"]* — handles dots, hyphens, any non-quote char including qualified addresses
  - Malformed body content (unclosed tags, angle brackets, XML snippets) does not cause parse failure — body is opaque
  - ATTR_RE uses LazyLock — compiled once, thread-safe
  - mentions= is comma-split; empty elements filtered; empty string → empty Vec
LOOK: ATTR_RE pattern; parse_attrs; require_attr
CHK: cargo test parser; verify raw preservation tests pass
UW: Regex::new(...).unwrap() — pattern is a compile-time constant, safe to unwrap
